## Summary
This documentation explains how to integrate Slack with Amplitude, allowing users to receive Amplitude updates in Slack channels, view expanded previews of charts and dashboards, get notifications about Amplitude Data project changes, and receive comment notifications when mentioned. It details the setup process for both personal connections and team space integrations.

